# Privacy Policy for Gondi Word Inserter

## Introduction
The Gondi Word Inserter is a browser extension developed by Navgurukul Foundation for Social Welfare. It helps users learn English words by inserting Gondi translations on web pages. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you use our extension.

## Information Collection
The Gondi Word Inserter extension:
- Does not collect or store any personal information
- Does not track your browsing history
- Does not transmit your data to external servers
- Only processes text content on web pages you visit while the extension is active

## Local Storage
The extension uses Chrome's storage API to:
- Store your preferences (such as whether the extension is enabled)
- Store dictionary data locally for performance optimization

## Permissions
The extension requires the following permissions:
- `activeTab`: To modify and process text on the currently active webpage
- `scripting`: To inject the translation functionality
- `storage`: To save your extension preferences

## Data Security
Since we don't collect user data, there are no associated security risks. All processing occurs locally on your device.

## Changes to Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy as the extension evolves. Significant changes will be communicated through the extension's update notes.

## Contact Information
For questions about this Privacy Policy or the Gondi Word Inserter extension, please contact:

**Navgurukul Foundation for Social Welfare**  
Email: hi@navgurukul.org  
